title: UEFA Champions League Highlights 2014-03-11 720p 50fps x264.wAm
description:
SPORT: UEFA Champions League
On: itv Central HD   
Date: Tuesday 11th March 2014

Extra Time.
Matt Smith presents highlights of tonight's second-leg games, with studio guests Lee Dixon and Andy Townsend. Arsenal have a tough task ahead following their 2-0 loss to Bayern Munich in the first leg, but Arsene Wenger's team travel to Germany hoping for a repeat of their victory there last season. Atletico Madrid will be favourites to beat AC Milan, having scored a late winner against them in Italy.

Captured and encoded at 50fps, which for sport is way better than the standard 25fps.
